content.p: Global Internship Programmes AIESEC Description: AIESEC is the world's largest youth-run leadership organisation which provide its members with an integrated development experience comprised of leadership opportunities, international traineeships and participation in a global learning environment. Focused on providing a platform for youth leadership development, AIESEC offers young people the opportunity to be global citizens, to change the world, and to get experience and skills that matter today. AIESEC is currently present in 12 universities in Malaysia: This programme offers international internships that contribute to your professional development and assist you to specialise in a certain field of work. Enhance your professional development by having an education, management or technical internship in one of over 110 countries for a duration of 6 to 18 months! What can you gain?
